snippet.title: House Party x Doja Cat - Coming Fall 2022!
snippet.description:
This Fall, after House Party leaves Early Access, Doja Cat is joining the cast of House Party, starring in her very own DLC expansion pack, adding tons of new content to the House Party base game and Original Story!

Wishlist the Doja Cat DLC here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1648810/House_Party__Doja_Cat_Expansion_Pack/

Check out House Party:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/611790/House_Party/

Talk about it on our Discord Community here:
https://discord.com/invite/eekgames

And here's our Twitter for good measure:
https://twitter.com/EekGamesLLC
